---
layout: base.njk
title: How old will you be when your home expires?
description: LIHTC affordability lasts 30 years. The people who move in don't stop needing a home after 30 years. Do the arithmetic.
---

<style>

  .eyebrow{display:inline-block;background:#ffffff14;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:999px;
    font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase}
  h1{font-size:46px;line-height:1.08;font-weight:800;margin:20px auto 0;max-width:17ch}
  h1 span{color:var(--gold)}
  header p{margin:20px auto 0;font-size:19px;color:#dbe4f0;max-width:56ch;line-height:1.7}

  main{padding:0 0 80px}
  .panel{
    background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:28px;
    padding:36px;margin-top:-32px;box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(31,59,109,.10);
  }
  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
  label{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:8px}
  .hint{font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:500;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;margin-top:4px}
  input,select{
    width:100%;padding:15px 16px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid var(--line);
    background:var(--cream);font-family:inherit;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);
  }
  input:focus,select:focus{outline:3px solid var(--gold);border-color:transparent}

  .go{
    width:100%;margin-top:26px;background:var(--navy);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:16px;
    padding:18px;font-family:inherit;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
  }
